fields.title:
Hi {{hidden:first_name}}, welcome back to module two of your company evaluation! 

To allocate the this to the right company, please enter your Company ID. This number will be required at the beginning of every module to link the data to your personal profile.

The Company ID can be found in your Impact Rooms on the right hand side of your dashboard.

properties.description: The number will look like CO123456

fields.title: Business Information

properties.description:
Thanks, {{hidden:first_name}}!

Now that we have covered the basics, lets look into {{hidden:company_name}}in a bit more detail.

fields.title: That's Compliance done {{hidden:first_name}}, what I will be asking in the next section section is about your business & revenue model, product description, vison, key milestones and strengths & weaknesses.
What is {{hidden:company_name}}'s type of business model?
As you selected 'Other' {{hidden:first_name}}, please tell me what type of business model your company has.
In a few sentences, describe {{hidden:company_name}}'s revenue model
What is the business vision?

properties.description: i.e. how is the company going to grow and expand and make money? Where will it be in 3-5 years?

fields.title: What key milestones has {{hidden:company_name}}  achieved to date?

properties.description: I am looking for things like time to MVP, customers acquired in X time, cash flow positive after X months, anchor customer signed up, etc.

fields.title: What are {{hidden:company_name}}'s strengths?

properties.description:
List a maximum 5 points.

A strength can be location, team, first to market, experienced team, IP that is patented,

fields.title: What are {{hidden:company_name}}'s weaknesses?

properties.description:
List a maximum 5 points.

A weakness is NOT a lack of people or finances. Weaknesses are things the management sees in their business that are a problem or not optimal that they can do something about given time and money.
